w electronics, but still\ncompatible with the present system, is planned to be inserted in ATLAS already\nin mid 2014 (at the end of the Phase~0 upgrade).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 May 2013 23:39:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-07"}
